<L>__{interior slave shack day}
<A>__{we see a sharp object scratching onto a surface. the tool moves on to form another mark. the sound is repetitive and almost unbearable. as we move out, we see the names anne, margaret, alonzo. they are engraved onto the violin, in the hidden area where solomon would rest his chin. solomon looks at it for a moment, moving his fingertips across the engraving. his face full of loss. sadly, he lifts his instrument under his chin and leaning his head to the side as if to play.}
